<br>
But we should have a significant greater power output then any other nuking class and that is ot the fact at the moment.<br>
Our mana efficiency should be superior at ALL levels and that is as well not reality yet. And superior mean not by a difference of 0.1, heh.<br>
<br>
We should be able to KILL Mobs without major difficulty if the tank and the chanter is dead. But we can't. We should be the nuking life assurance to a group in trouble. But we AREN'T.<br>
<br>
That is the class definition... nothing else.<br>
